Sentencas: A samaria-doped ceria (SDC) interlayer was used to avoid unfavorable solid-state reactions when using La(Sr)CoO3 (LSC) as a cathode on yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte.
Titulo: High performance electrode for medium-temperature solid oxide fuel cells -: La(Sr)CoO3 cathode with ceria interlayer on zirconia electrolyte

Sentencas: A porous LSC cathode prepared on a thin and dense SDC interlayer exhibited very high performance even at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: High performance electrode for medium-temperature solid oxide fuel cells -: La(Sr)CoO3 cathode with ceria interlayer on zirconia electrolyte

Sentencas: The performance was enhanced further by dispersing a small amount of nanometer-sized Pt catalysts on the LSC surface.
Titulo: High performance electrode for medium-temperature solid oxide fuel cells -: La(Sr)CoO3 cathode with ceria interlayer on zirconia electrolyte

Sentencas: The current density on the Pt-LSC cathode at an overpotential of -0.05 V was 0.6 A/cm(2) at 800 degrees C in O-2.
Titulo: High performance electrode for medium-temperature solid oxide fuel cells -: La(Sr)CoO3 cathode with ceria interlayer on zirconia electrolyte
